acks}}\n\n{{coord|37|58|58|N|89|13|23|W|region:US_type:landmark|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Motorsport venues in Illinois]]\n[[Category:ARCA Menards Series tracks]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Perry County, Illinois]]\n[[Category:Tourist attractions in Perry County, Illinois]]\n\n{{Autoracing-venue-stub}}\n{{Illinois-stadium-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Luks25", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DuQuoin_State_Fairgrounds_Racetrack"}
{"title_page": "Bark Lake (Ontario)", "text_new": "{{Infobox lake\n| name         = Bark Lake\n| image        = Bark Lake on a summer evening (38831993252).jpg\n| caption      = \n| image_bathymetry  = \n| caption_bathymetry= \n| location          = [[South Algonquin, Ontario|Township of South Algonquin]]\n| coords            = {{coord|45|27|N|77|50|W|region:CA-ON_type:waterbody|display=inline,title}}\n| type              = \n| inflow            = [[Madawaska River (Ontario)|Madawaska River]], [[Opeongo River]]\n| outflow           = [[Madawaska River (Ontario)|Madawaska River]]\n| catchment         = \n| basin_countries   = Canada\n| length            = {{convert|14.0|km|mi|1|abbr=on}}\n| width             = {{convert|6.0|km|mi|1|abbr=on}}\n| area              = \n| depth             = \n| max-depth         = \n| volume            = \n| residence_time    = \n| shore             = \n| elevation         = {{convert|450|m|ft|0|abbr=on}}\n| islands           = \n| cities            = \n| frozen            = \n}}\n'''Bark Lake''' is a [[lake]] in the [[South Algonquin, Ontario|Township of South Algonquin]], in [[Nipissing District, Ontario|Nipissing District]] in [[Ontario]], [[Canada]]. It lies near [[Madawaska, Ontario]] on the [[Madawaska River (Ontario)|Madawaska River]] where the tributary [[Opeongo River]] joins. An [[episode]] of ''[[Naked and Afraid]]'' was [[filmed]] here.<ref>https://www.channelguidemag.com/tv-news/2016/03/20/recap-naked-afraid-canada-episode-2/</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of lakes in Ontario]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n*Government of Canada - Topographic Map sheet 031F05 - retrieved 2007-11-02 via [http://atlas.nrcan.gc.ca/ Atlas of Canada]\n\n==External links==\n* {{Commons cat inline|Bark Lake|Bark Lake (Ontario)}}\n\n[[Category:Lakes of Nipissing District]]\n\n\n{{NorthernOntario-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox lake\n| name         = Bark Lake\n| image        = Bark Lake on a summer evening (38831993252).jpg\n| caption      